sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Actor
    participant S as Server
    participant L as EventStore
    participant H as HashEngine
    participant AL as AuditLog
    participant ES as StateSnapshot

    A->>S: Perform action eg update salary
    activate S

    S->>S: Execute domain mutation via Prisma

    S->>L: Create Event record
    activate L
    Note over L: action, actorId, targetId,<br/>details, timestamp

    L->>AL: Fetch latest AuditLog entry
    AL-->>L: previousHash from last entry

    L->>H: Compute hash
    activate H
    Note over H: input = previousHash +<br/>action + target +<br/>user + timestamp +<br/>JSON.stringify details
    H->>H: SHA-256 digest
    H-->>L: hash = a3f7c9e2...
    deactivate H

    L->>AL: INSERT audit entry
    Note over AL: Immutable: no UPDATE<br/>or DELETE allowed

    L->>ES: Upsert state snapshot
    Note over ES: Materialized view of<br/>current entity state<br/>version incremented

    deactivate L

    S-->>A: Response with audit ID
    deactivate S

    Note over AL: Hash Chain Integrity:<br/>Entry N.previousHash ===<br/>Entry N-1 hash.<br/>Any tampering breaks chain.
